00:00:16.021 --> 00:00:19.860
Then I'll regroup my two x terms together 
on the left hand side,

00:00:19.860 --> 00:00:24.353
and I'll regroup my two y terms on the
left hand side as well.

00:00:24.353 --> 00:00:30.006
Now I'm ready to complete the square for the x terms
and the y terms.

00:00:30.006 --> 00:00:32.806
