00:00:32.806 --> 00:00:35.804
and we addd 9 to complete the square for the y terms.

00:00:35.804 --> 00:00:38.579
Keep in mind we also need to add 4 and 9

00:00:38.579 --> 00:00:40.578
to the right hand side of our equation

00:00:40.578 --> 00:00:42.894
to make sure it's balanced.

00:00:42.894 --> 00:00:46.984
So, these three terms can be written as x - 2 squared

00:00:46.984 --> 00:00:50.688
these three terms can be written as y + 3 squared

00:00:50.688 --> 00:00:55.667
and then we simply combine these three terms to get +16.

00:00:55.667 --> 00:00:58.973
